ZH: 万物皆有生命。
EN: All things have life.

ZH: 万物互相依存。
EN: All things are interdependent.

ZH: 万物皆为一体。
EN: All things are integrated as one.

ZH: 万物都在不断变化。
EN: All things are constantly changing.

ZH: 万物都有其存在的价值。
EN: All things have their own value of existence.

ZH: 万物的美都是独特的。
EN: The beauty of all things is unique.

ZH: 万物有其内在的规律。
EN: All things have their own internal laws.

ZH: 万物之间存在着因果关系。
EN: There is a causal relationship between all things.

ZH: 万物存在于时间和空间之中。
EN: All things exist in time and space.

ZH: 万物的存在是相互影响的。
EN: The existence of all things is interrelated.

ZH: 万物在自然界中相互作用。
EN: All things interact with each other in nature.

ZH: 万物都受到环境的影响。
EN: All things are influenced by the environment.

ZH: 万物之间存在着平衡。
EN: There is a balance between all things.

ZH: 万物都具有共通之处。
EN: All things have something in common.

ZH: 在宇宙中，万物互相联结。
EN: In the universe, all things are interconnected.

ZH: 万物都是宇宙的奇迹。
EN: All things are miracles of the universe.

ZH: 万物都有其独特的目的。
EN: All things have their unique purpose.

ZH: 万物的存在给我们带来了无尽的惊奇。
EN: The existence of all things brings us endless wonder.

ZH: 万物的多样性使世界更加美丽。
EN: The diversity of all things makes the world more beautiful.

ZH: 万物的存在使我们有了生命的体验。
EN: The existence of all things gives us the experience of life.
